Subject: [PATCH] pin Go toolchain for reproducible monorepo builds

A tip-layer local modification, applied on top of the structurally-rewritten
mirror. Rebased onto the new tip on every import.

---
diff --git a/go.mod b/go.mod
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/go.mod
+++ b/go.mod
@@ -1,5 +1,7 @@
 module acme/widget

 go 1.21
+
+toolchain go1.21.6
